  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>General</Type>
    <Text>Hotel has fitness room, Esthetica natural therapies center, large outdoor swimming pool.  As the name suggests the hotel is well known for its convention capability.  There are altogether 11 conference rooms with the maximum capacity of 1800 pax. The hotel is close to some famous golf courses such as Pinehurst, Alpine and Muang Ake golf club all within 30-45 minutes drive. A suitable hotel for both FIT and group clientele. (09/06SW)</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>SurroundingArea</Type>
    <Text>The hotel is located in Don Muang district 25 kilometres north of the city centre. Hotel is accessible by 2 ways. The first access is by entering via the North Park golf club and the second access is at Laksi Plaza junction.  It takes about 20 minutes drive from city to hotel by express way. It is 50 kilometres away from Suvarnabhumi airport.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>RoomTypes</Type>
    <Text>Superior rooms are large and tastefully decorated with new closet design. There are 2 television available in the rooms.  One is in front of the bed and the other in the bathroom.  A see-through bathroom is large and built with black granite. The colour tone of the room are white and offset with light brown soft wood. All rooms have coffee/tea making facility.  Welcome drink and fruit plate is served upon arrival. All rooms has window at the side overlooking city view.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>PropertyInformation</Type>
    <Text>It is a high rise 16 storey building connected with a 5 storey convention building.  The connection of two building are on the 5th floor of convention building and 6th floor of hotel building.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>DiningFacilities</Type>
    <Text>The hotel's restaurants include Tex Mex all day dinning coffee shop, adjacent to the reception area. The China Moon exquisite Cantonese delicacies and Get ready Pub and disco are on the second floor.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>Short</Type>
    <Text>Lobby is large with limited seating area. The lobby is open to the road in front.</Text>
  </Description>
